<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Password Reset</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>Hi <%= @user.first_name %>,</p>

    <p>Someone requested a password reset. Click on the link below if you recognize the activity. The link expires in 15 minutes.</p>
    <p><a href="https://embloy.com/password-reset/new?reset_token=<%= @token %>">Reset your password</a></p>

    <p>If you did not request this change, you can safely ignore this email.</p>

    <p>Best,<br>
    The Embloy Team</p>

    <br>
    <p><em>This is an automated message, please do not reply to this email.</em></p>
  </body>
</html>
